TITLE: TypeScript Usage of useGetOneLive Hook with Generic Types
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the useGetOneLive hook with TypeScript generic parameters for type safety. This example defines Ticket and User interfaces and uses them to provide type safety for the fetched data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/marmelab/react-admin/blob/master/docs/useGetOneLive.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

