TITLE: Accessing Markdown Editor Instance in React-Admin using TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Example component demonstrating how to access the Markdown editor instance using refs and retrieve markdown content. The component includes a button to get the current markdown value and display it in an alert. Uses the @react-admin/ra-markdown package along with Material-UI components.
SOURCE: https://github.com/marmelab/react-admin/blob/master/docs/MarkdownInput.md#2025-04-20_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: tsx
