TITLE: Programmatically Changing ReferenceOneInput Values
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating how to programmatically change a reference record's values using react-hook-form's setValue method and the useSourceContext hook for obtaining the correct field names.
SOURCE: https://github.com/marmelab/react-admin/blob/master/docs/ReferenceOneInput.md#2025-04-20_snippet_9

