TITLE: Replacing SearchResultItem in React Admin
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to completely replace the default SearchResultItem with a custom component, allowing for full control over the rendering of each search result.
SOURCE: https://github.com/marmelab/react-admin/blob/master/docs/SearchWithResult.md#2025-04-20_snippet_13

